{"title":"SQL语言基础2","slug":"2019-01-29-sql2","date":"2019-01-29T02:35:53.000Z","updated":"2019-01-30T01:42:32.100Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019-01-29-sql2.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h4 id=\"TOP子句\"><a href=\"#TOP子句\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"TOP子句\"></a>TOP子句</h4><ul>\n<li><p><code>TOP</code>子句用于规定返回的记录的数目，语法：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> TOP <span class=\"built_in\">number</span>|<span class=\"keyword\">percent</span> column_name(s) <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> table_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>MySQL</code>语法为</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表名称 <span class=\"keyword\">LIMIT</span> 数目</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-LIKE操作符\"><a href=\"#SQL-LIKE操作符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL LIKE操作符\"></a>SQL LIKE操作符</h4><ul>\n<li><p><code>LIKE</code>操作符用于在<code>WHERE</code>子句中搜索列中指定模式，语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表名称 <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">LIKE</span> 模式</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>使用<code>NOT</code>关键字，可选取不符合制定模式的列，例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> * <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> City <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"keyword\">LIKE</span> <span class=\"string\">'%LON%'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-通配符\"><a href=\"#SQL-通配符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL 通配符\"></a>SQL 通配符</h4><ul>\n<li>在搜索数据库时，可以使用SQL通配符，通配符可以代替一个或多个字符。通配符必须与LIKE一起使用</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>| 通配符      | 描述                     |<br>| ———– | ———————— |<br>| %           | 替代一个或多个字符       |<br>| _           | 替代一个字符             |<br>| [charlist]  | 替代字符列中任意一个字符 |<br>| [^charlist] | 不再字符列中的任意字符   |</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"IN操作符\"><a href=\"#IN操作符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"IN操作符\"></a>IN操作符</h4><ul>\n<li><p>IN操作符允许我们在WHERE子句中规定多个值，语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表名称 <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">IN</span> （值<span class=\"number\">1</span>，值<span class=\"number\">2.</span>。。）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> * <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> LastName <span class=\"keyword\">IN</span> (<span class=\"string\">'Adams'</span>,<span class=\"string\">'Carter'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"BETWEEN-操作符\"><a href=\"#BETWEEN-操作符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BETWEEN 操作符\"></a>BETWEEN 操作符</h4><ul>\n<li><p><code>BETWEEN</code>操作符用于在<code>WHERE</code>子句中选取介于两个值的数据，组合使用<code>BETWEEN</code>和<code>AND</code>，语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表名称 <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">BETWEEN</span> 值<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">AND</span> 值<span class=\"number\">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>也可使用<code>NOT</code>选取范围之外的数值</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-Alias\"><a href=\"#SQL-Alias\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL Alias\"></a>SQL Alias</h4><ul>\n<li><p>通过使用<code>SQL Alias</code>可以为列和表指定别名，表的语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表名称 <span class=\"keyword\">AS</span> 别名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>例子</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> po.OrderID , p.LastName , p.FirstName <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons <span class=\"keyword\">AS</span> P, Product_Orders <span class=\"keyword\">AS</span> po <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> p.LastName = <span class=\"string\">'Adams'</span> <span class=\"keyword\">AND</span> p.FirstName = <span class=\"string\">'Jojn'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>列的语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称 <span class=\"keyword\">AS</span> 别名 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>例子</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> LastName <span class=\"keyword\">AS</span> Family , FirstName <span class=\"keyword\">AS</span> <span class=\"keyword\">Name</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-join\"><a href=\"#SQL-join\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL join\"></a>SQL join</h4><ul>\n<li><p><code>SQL join</code>用于根据两个或多个表中的列之间的关系，从这些表中查询数据。数据库中的表可通过键将彼此联系起来，主键(Primary Key)是一个列，在这个列中的每一行的值都是唯一的。可以通过引用两个表，从两个表中获取数据，例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> Persons.LastName, Persons.FirstName, Orders.OrderNo</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons, Orders</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> Persons.Id_P = Orders.Id_P</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-INNER-JOIN\"><a href=\"#SQL-INNER-JOIN\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL INNER JOIN\"></a>SQL INNER JOIN</h4><ul>\n<li><p>返回多个表中关键字匹配的行。语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">INNER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 表<span class=\"number\">2</span> <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1.</span>列 = 表<span class=\"number\">2.</span>列</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-LEFT-JOIN\"><a href=\"#SQL-LEFT-JOIN\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL LEFT JOIN\"></a>SQL LEFT JOIN</h4><ul>\n<li><p>会从左表中返回所有行，即使在右表中没有匹配的行。语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">LEFT</span> <span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 表<span class=\"number\">2</span> <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1.</span>列 = 表<span class=\"number\">2.</span>列</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-RIGHT-JOIN\"><a href=\"#SQL-RIGHT-JOIN\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL RIGHT JOIN\"></a>SQL RIGHT JOIN</h4><ul>\n<li><p>会从有表中返回所有行，即使在左表中没有匹配的行，语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">RIGHT</span> <span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 表<span class=\"number\">2</span> <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1.</span>列 = 表<span class=\"number\">2.</span>列</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-FULL-JOIN\"><a href=\"#SQL-FULL-JOIN\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL FULL JOIN\"></a>SQL FULL JOIN</h4><ul>\n<li><p>会从左表和右表返回所有的行，语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名称<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FULL</span> <span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 表<span class=\"number\">2</span> <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1.</span>列 = 表<span class=\"number\">2.</span>列</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-UNION操作符\"><a href=\"#SQL-UNION操作符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL UNION操作符\"></a>SQL UNION操作符</h4><ul>\n<li><p>用于合并两个或多个<code>SELECT</code>语句的结果集。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>UNION</code>内部的<code>SELECT</code>语句必须拥有相同数量的列，列也必须拥有相似的数据类型，每条<code>SELECT</code>语句中的列的顺序必须相同。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表<span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">UNION</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 列名 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 表<span class=\"number\">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>默认情况下，<code>UNION</code>不包含重复元素，若要选取重复元素，则使用<code>UNION ALL</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"keyword\">COL</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> TABLE1</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">UNION</span> ALL</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"keyword\">COL</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> TABLE2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>UNION</code>结果集的列名总是等于第一个<code>SELECT</code>结果的列名</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-SELECT-INTO\"><a href=\"#SQL-SELECT-INTO\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL SELECT INTO\"></a>SQL SELECT INTO</h4><ul>\n<li><p>用于从一个表中选取数据，然后插入到另一个表中。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>常用于创建表的备份附件和对记录进行存档，例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> * <span class=\"keyword\">INTO</span> Persons_backup <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> * <span class=\"keyword\">INTO</span> <span class=\"keyword\">IN</span> <span class=\"string\">'Backup.mdb'</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> LastName,FirstName <span class=\"keyword\">INTO</span> Persons_backup <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>实例2，带有<code>WHERE</code>子句</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> LastName , FirstName <span class=\"keyword\">INTO</span> Persons_backup <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> City=<span class=\"string\">'Beijing'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>实例3，被连接的表</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> Persons.LastName,Orders.OrderNo <span class=\"keyword\">INTO</span> Persons_Order_Back <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> Persons <span class=\"keyword\">INNER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> Orders <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> Persons.Id = Orders.Id</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-CREATE-DATABASE\"><a href=\"#SQL-CREATE-DATABASE\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL CREATE DATABASE\"></a>SQL CREATE DATABASE</h4><ul>\n<li><p>创建数据库，语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">DATABASE</span> db_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-CREATE-TABLE\"><a href=\"#SQL-CREATE-TABLE\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL CREATE TABLE\"></a>SQL CREATE TABLE</h4><ul>\n<li><p>创建表，语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> table_name (</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcol1 datatype,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcol2 datatype,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t....</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>实例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> Persons (</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">Id</span> <span class=\"built_in\">int</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tLastName <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tFirstName <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tAddress <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tCity <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-Constraints\"><a href=\"#SQL-Constraints\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL Constraints\"></a>SQL Constraints</h4><ul>\n<li><p>SQL 约束用于限制加入表的数据的类型，可以在创建表时规定约束，也可以在创建完成后添加</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>NOT NULL约束强制列不接受NULL值，也就是强制字段始终包含值，如果不向字段添加值，就无法插入新纪录或更新记录。例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> Persons</span><br><span class=\"line\">(</span><br><span class=\"line\">Id_P <span class=\"built_in\">int</span> <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">LastName <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">FirstName <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>),</span><br><span class=\"line\">Address <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>),</span><br><span class=\"line\">City <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>UNIQUE约束唯一标识数据库表中的每条记录，每个表可以有多个UNIQUE约束。MySQL创建表时添加UNIQUE约束</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> Persons</span><br><span class=\"line\">(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Id_P <span class=\"built_in\">int</span> <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    LastName <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t...</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">UNIQUE</span> (Id_P)</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>PRIMARY KEY约束唯一标识数据库表中的每条记录，主键必须包含唯一的值，主键列不能包含NULL值，每个表都应该且只应该有一个主键。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> Persons</span><br><span class=\"line\">(</span><br><span class=\"line\">Id_P <span class=\"built_in\">int</span> <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">LastName <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br><span class=\"line\">PRIMARY <span class=\"keyword\">KEY</span> (Id_P)</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>FOREIGN KEY约束，一个表中的FOREIGN KEY指向另一个表中的PRIMARY KEY，例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> Orders</span><br><span class=\"line\">(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Id_O <span class=\"built_in\">int</span> <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    OrderNo <span class=\"built_in\">int</span> <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t...</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">FOREIGN</span> <span class=\"keyword\">KEY</span> (Id_P) <span class=\"keyword\">REFERENCES</span> Persons(Id_P)</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>CHECK约束用于限制列中的值的数据范围。例</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> Persons</span><br><span class=\"line\">(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Id_P <span class=\"built_in\">int</span> <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    LastName <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"> \t...</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">CHECK</span> (Id_P&gt;<span class=\"number\">0</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>DEFAULT约束，用于向列中插入默认值，如果没有规定其他的值，那么会将默认值添加到所有新纪录。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"CREATE-INDEX\"><a href=\"#CREATE-INDEX\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CREATE INDEX\"></a>CREATE INDEX</h4><ul>\n<li><p>索引可以在不读取整个表的情况下，更快的查找数据。语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">INDEX</span> index_name <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> table_name(<span class=\"keyword\">column</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>创建唯一索引</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">UNIQUE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">INDEX</span> index_name <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> table_name(<span class=\"keyword\">column</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL撤销索引，表及数据库\"><a href=\"#SQL撤销索引，表及数据库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL撤销索引，表及数据库\"></a>SQL撤销索引，表及数据库</h4><ul>\n<li><p>SQL DROP INDEX删除表中的索引</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">ALTER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> table_name <span class=\"keyword\">DROP</span> <span class=\"keyword\">INDEX</span> index_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>SQL DROP TABLE删除表</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">DROP</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> table_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>SQL DROP DATABASE删除数据库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">DROP</span> <span class=\"keyword\">DATABASE</span> db_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>SQL TRUNCATE TABLE 删除表中的数据而不删除表本身</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">TRUNCATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> table_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-ALTER-TABLE\"><a href=\"#SQL-ALTER-TABLE\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL ALTER TABLE\"></a>SQL ALTER TABLE</h4><ul>\n<li><p>用于在已有的表中添加，修改或删除列。添加列语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">ALTER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> table_name <span class=\"keyword\">ADD</span> column_name datatype</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>删除列语法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">ALTER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> table_name <span class=\"keyword\">DROP</span> <span class=\"keyword\">COLUMN</span> column_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>修改表中列的数据类型</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">ALTER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> table_name <span class=\"keyword\">ALTER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">COLUMN</span> column_name datatype</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"AUTO-INCREMENT\"><a href=\"#AUTO-INCREMENT\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"AUTO INCREMENT\"></a>AUTO INCREMENT</h4><ul>\n<li><p>每次插入新纪录时，自动的创建主键字段的值，可以在表中创建一个AUTO_INCREMENT字段</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> Persons</span><br><span class=\"line\">(</span><br><span class=\"line\">P_Id <span class=\"built_in\">int</span> <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span> AUTO_INCREMENT,</span><br><span class=\"line\">LastName <span class=\"built_in\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">NOT</span> <span class=\"literal\">NULL</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br><span class=\"line\">PRIMARY <span class=\"keyword\">KEY</span> (P_Id)</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置起始值，<code>ALTER TABLE Persons AUTO_INCREMENT=100</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"SQL-CREATE-VIEW\"><a href=\"#SQL-CREATE-VIEW\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL CREATE VIEW\"></a>SQL CREATE VIEW</h4><ul>\n<li>视图，是基于SQL语句的结果集的可视化的表。视图包含行和列，其中的字段就是来自一个或多个数据库中的真实的表中的字段。可以向视图中添加SQL函数，WHERE及JOIN语句，也可以向其提交数据，就像这些。。。。。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>#### </p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"SQL","slug":"SQL","count":3,"path":"api/tags/SQL.json"}]}